N . Korea to respond soon on talks proposal . North Korea has told the United States and South Korea that it will soon be ready to respond to a proposal for four - party talks on the future of the Korean peninsula , the State Department said on Monday . " The North Koreans indicated that they will be prepared soon to give the United States and the Republic of ( South ) Korea a formal response to our joint briefing " on the talks proposal , spokesman Nicholas Burns told a news briefing . 
